      <td>+</td>
      <td>-0.6</td>
      <td>+</td>
      <td>0.9</td>
      <td>+</td>
      <td>0.7</td>
      <td>+</td>
      <td>-0.8</td>
      <td>= 4.8.  For L1 Norm, they both look about the same, and generally will lean towards the former.</td>
